mathematica: b[n_, k_] := b[n, k] = If[n<2, If[k<n, 0, 1], Sum[Binomial[n-1, r]*b[r, k-1]*b[n-1-r, k-1], {r, 0, n-1}]]; a[n_] := b[2*n, n] - b[2*n, n-1]; Table[a[n], {n, 0, 20}] (* _Jean-François Alcover_, Feb 25 2017, translated from Maple *)
